The '''Nocturne of the Winged-Stars''' was a natural phenomenon on [[Caluula/Legends|Caluula]] that occurred once every 300 years. The event of [[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]] was disrupted by the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. The [[winged-star]]s were wiped out by the [[Alpha Red (pathogen)|Alpha Red virus]].

